The project was introduced on Wednesday evening, one of them clarifies.
The Ministry of Nature confirmed that the project was submitted to the government.
Deputy Prime Minister Alexander Khloponin, a representative of the supervising subsoil use, said that the project has not yet been submitted to the official's staff.
"The auction can be announced in August, immediately after the government's order is released, and taking into account the deadline for the applications of potential participants (at least 45 days) the tender can be held in October," the Ministry of Nature says.
