Tax notices on the transport tax will cease to be sent by mail - website Behind the wheel www.zr.ru
Tax inspection has changed the procedure for sending notifications about property taxes.
All Russian car owners are accustomed to the scheme that has not changed for years: in summer and autumn they receive by mail receipts for payment of transport tax for the previous year.
However, this year many of them will not wait.
The fact is that the tax office without too much noise has changed the order of notification of citizens.
Those who are registered in the "Personal account of the taxpayer" on the official website of the agency nalog.ru, the notifications will come in electronic form.
In the inspection automatically considered such Russians online users and deleted them from the standard, "paper" mailing.
The innovation will affect all owners of vehicles and real estate.
All the others will still receive familiar letters.
However, the ability to return to the old scheme and the owners of the account on the site.
To do this, they will have to visit the department of the tax service during August and write an application.
On the one hand, the new order is more modern and convenient.
The notification will appear in the "personal cabinet" immediately after the compilation, while the letter will go for several days and may be completely lost.
In addition, the number of users of the Internet service tax inspection exceeded 18 million people, which will allow the agency to seriously save on mailing.
On the other hand, modest news on the inspection website is clearly not enough to inform citizens about the changed procedure.
Some could register in the "personal account" to receive a one-time service and have long forgotten about it.
These people will not wait for the notice by mail and, without knowing it themselves, fall into the category of non-payers with all the ensuing consequences.
Access to the "Personal account of the taxpayer" is carried out in three ways: through the account of the portal gosuslugi.ru, by electronic signature or entering the login and password specified in the registration card.
The last can be obtained in person in any department of the tax inspection (regardless of the place of registration).
We remind you that this year the transport tax must be paid before December 1.
The newsletter of notifications began in July.
